OL,3,CRyanair says fares 'unlikely' to grow
OL,4,Cover key summer months
OL,6,FBudget airline Ryanair has said fares
OL,7,Fare unlikely to grow over the key
OL,8,Fsummer months amid consumer
OL,9,Funcertainty caused by the war in Iran
OL,11,FThe Irish carrier said it had been
OL,12,Fexpecting low, single-digit increases
OL,13,Fin air fares in its peak season, but
OL,14,Fis now seeing pricing trend "broadly
OL,15,Fflat" between July and September.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/6
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,310,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30902
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1779123960
OL,3,CRyanair says fares 'unlikely' to grow
OL,4,Cover key summer months
OL,6,FIt said: "Pricing in recent weeks has
OL,7,Feased somewhat in response to economic
OL,8,Funcertainty caused by higher oil
OL,9,Fprices, the fear of fuel shortages and
OL,10,Fthe risk of inflation adversely
OL,11,Fimpacting consumer spending."
OL,13,FThe group said while it has secured
OL,14,Fpricing for 80% of its jet fuel needs,
OL,15,Fthe cost of the remaining 20% has
OL,16,F"spiked" due to the Middle East
OL,17,Fconflict and cautioned that if prices
OL,18,Fremain where they are, then its costs
OL,19,Fcould jump by a "mid-single digit"
OL,20,Fpercentage in 2026-27.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/6
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,310,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30903
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1779123960
OL,3,CRyanair says fares 'unlikely' to grow
OL,4,Cover key summer months
OL,6,FRyanair posted an after-tax profit of
OL,7,F2.26 billion euros (#1.96 billion) for
OL,8,Fthe year to March 31, which is
OL,9,Fslightly better than expected.
OL,11,FIt said it was "far too early" to give
OL,12,Fan outlook for the new financial year,
OL,13,Fgiven the uncertainty over demand and
OL,14,Ffuel prices.
OL,16,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,17,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,18,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,19,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/6
