FL,310,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30904
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1779123960
OL,3,CRyanair says fares 'unlikely' to grow
OL,4,Cover key summer months
OL,6,FCEO Michael O'Leary said European
OL,7,Fairlines were sourcing their jet fuel
OL,8,Ffrom alternative countries to overcome
OL,9,Fthe supply shock caused by Iran's
OL,10,Fblockade of the crucial Strait of
OL,11,FHormuz.
OL,13,FHe said: "The conflict in the Middle
OL,14,FEast has created economic uncertainty
OL,15,Fand we still don't know when the
OL,16,FStrait of Hormuz will reopen.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/6
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,310,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30905
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1779123960
OL,3,CRyanair says fares 'unlikely' to grow
OL,4,Cover key summer months
OL,6,F"Despite this, Europe remains
OL,7,Frelatively well supplied with jet-
OL,8,Ffuel, with significant volumes sourced
OL,9,Ffrom west Africa, the Americas, and
OL,10,FNorway."
OL,12,FLike other airlines, the group said
OL,13,Fbookings were increasingly being made
OL,14,Fat the last minute, though it said
OL,15,Fdemand remained "robust".
OL,17,FIt is expecting to fly 4% more
OL,18,Fpassengers over the year to March
OL,19,F2027, at 216 million, matching the 4%
OL,20,Fgrowth it saw in 2025-26.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/6
